697
01:12:58,370 --> 01:12:59,830
Mr. Kim Ki Ja?

698
01:13:00,130 --> 01:13:02,100
Please go into room number two.

699
01:13:03,270 --> 01:13:04,740
Ms. Kim Soo Jung.

700
01:13:05,010 --> 01:13:06,770
- You can go to room number three. - Okay.

701
01:13:06,770 --> 01:13:08,180
Hello.

702
01:13:08,180 --> 01:13:10,310
(Doctor Ji Sun Woo)

703
01:13:25,260 --> 01:13:26,490
Is it serious?

704
01:13:26,930 --> 01:13:28,600
Should I just get admitted?

705
01:13:32,230 --> 01:13:35,870
Your fever came down, but you still have the coughs.

706
01:13:36,070 --> 01:13:37,670
Let's keep on taking the medication for a few more days.

707
01:13:46,880 --> 01:13:48,280
How's your insomnia?

708
01:13:48,520 --> 01:13:49,680
So-so.

709
01:13:49,850 --> 01:13:52,190
It's not bad enough to impact my daily life.

710
01:13:52,190 --> 01:13:53,820
Are you handling it with medication?

711
01:13:55,120 --> 01:13:57,760
Don't tell me you self-diagnosed and gave yourself a prescription.

712
01:14:02,830 --> 01:14:04,630
Are you trying to treat me?

713
01:14:05,730 --> 01:14:07,640
I don't intend on doing that,

714
01:14:07,640 --> 01:14:10,240
but I'm just curious if you're intending on using other methods.

715
01:14:13,210 --> 01:14:14,310
Dating.

716
01:14:15,280 --> 01:14:17,510
It's an easy and healthy method. What do you think?

717
01:14:18,380 --> 01:14:20,410
(Family Medicine Doctor Ji Sun Woo)

718
01:14:24,120 --> 01:14:25,820
Are you good enough to get rid of...

719
01:14:27,050 --> 01:14:29,020
someone's insomnia at once?

720
01:14:36,800 --> 01:14:38,400
Do you want to check?

721
01:14:40,900 --> 01:14:42,340
I'll try it.

722
01:14:43,770 --> 01:14:45,740
Although I don't know when that'll be.

723
01:14:48,210 --> 01:14:51,010
Anyway, thanks for your advice.

724
01:15:09,200 --> 01:15:11,870
Are you playing games again? Hurry up and go to class.

725
01:15:11,870 --> 01:15:13,270
- Yes, ma'am. - Yes, ma'am.

726
01:15:13,270 --> 01:15:14,700
Hold on, hold on.

727
01:15:15,500 --> 01:15:17,740
- Nice. - What are you doing?

728
01:15:17,740 --> 01:15:19,010
Where are you, son?

729
01:15:19,010 --> 01:15:20,510
Hey, just eat it.

730
01:15:20,510 --> 01:15:22,540
- Look at this. - Hey, hey.

731
01:15:22,540 --> 01:15:24,050
It was a mistake.

732
01:15:24,050 --> 01:15:25,580
(How did your test go?)

733
01:15:25,580 --> 01:15:28,720
How did your test go? Why aren't you answering me?

734
01:15:28,720 --> 01:15:31,550
(How did your test go? Why aren't you answering me?)

735
01:15:56,280 --> 01:15:57,410
I'll head out first.

736
01:15:57,410 --> 01:15:59,150
(Doctor Sul Myung Sook)

737
01:16:04,220 --> 01:16:05,220
Dr. Ji.

738
01:16:07,660 --> 01:16:09,490
What is it? Do you have something to say?

739
01:16:09,720 --> 01:16:10,760
Well...

740
01:16:12,830 --> 01:16:15,530
Don't take this the wrong way, okay?

741
01:16:18,270 --> 01:16:19,930
What is it? Why are you so hesitant?

742
01:16:21,500 --> 01:16:22,640
It's about Tae Oh.

743
01:16:24,040 --> 01:16:26,010
When does his restraining order end?

744
01:16:29,010 --> 01:16:30,750
It was for two years, so...

745
01:16:35,150 --> 01:16:38,020
Right? It's almost over, isn't it?

746
01:16:39,090 --> 01:16:40,150
You're right.

747
01:16:41,720 --> 01:16:43,620
I wasn't paying attention to it, so I forgot about it.

748
01:16:46,030 --> 01:16:47,290
Why do you ask?

749
01:16:48,630 --> 01:16:49,960
I was suddenly reminded of it.

750
01:16:51,600 --> 01:16:54,670
Does Joon Young talk to his dad at all?

751
01:16:55,740 --> 01:16:56,800
No.

752
01:16:57,370 --> 01:16:59,910
You know he hates his dad.

753
01:17:00,640 --> 01:17:03,040
I see. I'm glad.

754
01:17:09,280 --> 01:17:10,580
- See you tomorrow. - Okay.

755
01:17:24,800 --> 01:17:26,100
- Are you home? - Yes.

756
01:17:29,370 --> 01:17:31,340
That smells good.

757
01:17:38,710 --> 01:17:39,750
What is this?

758
01:17:54,500 --> 01:17:56,860
I'm not going to go. What about you?

759
01:17:58,100 --> 01:17:59,400
Of course, I won't go.

760
01:18:00,630 --> 01:18:01,840
Why would I go?

761
01:18:07,010 --> 01:18:08,910
- I'll go wash up. - Okay.

762
01:18:17,420 --> 01:18:20,190
Joon Young, why didn't you pick up your phone?

763
01:18:20,350 --> 01:18:21,760
I forgot I turned it off.

764
01:18:22,060 --> 01:18:24,590
Yeah right. I know you were playing games.

765
01:18:24,590 --> 01:18:25,760
Do you think I wouldn't know?

766
01:18:25,760 --> 01:18:28,030
Come on, I just finished my exams.

767
01:18:30,100 --> 01:18:31,970
Guess where I went today.

768
01:18:32,570 --> 01:18:33,630
Where?

769
01:18:34,370 --> 01:18:36,500
The new premium housing complex.

770
01:18:37,540 --> 01:18:40,170
I went to take a look because I heard it's really nice.

771
01:18:40,410 --> 01:18:42,410
Why? Are we moving?

772
01:18:43,180 --> 01:18:44,450
No.

773
01:18:45,980 --> 01:18:48,720
But it was really nice.

774
01:18:50,120 --> 01:18:52,290
Forget it. I like our house now.

775
01:18:52,890 --> 01:18:54,560
(To: Lee Joon Young)

776
01:19:02,930 --> 01:19:07,870
