777
01:19:35,000 --> 01:19:36,000
Mom?

778
01:19:36,860 --> 01:19:37,870
Mom?

779
01:19:38,700 --> 01:19:40,730
Hello? Mom?

780
01:19:43,000 --> 01:19:44,410
I said I have to go.

781
01:19:50,950 --> 01:19:55,080
(To: Lee Joon Young)

782
01:20:02,160 --> 01:20:07,530
(You're invited to Jenny's house party.)

783
01:20:32,990 --> 01:20:35,690
(A World of Married Couple)

784
01:20:35,690 --> 01:20:37,420
I heard he's back.

785
01:20:37,690 --> 01:20:39,930
The entire neighborhood is talking about Tae Oh's new movie...

786
01:20:39,930 --> 01:20:41,630
and how he's back.

787
01:20:41,760 --> 01:20:42,860
You look great.

788
01:20:43,300 --> 01:20:44,970
I knew you'd still look amazing.

789
01:20:45,030 --> 01:20:46,130
What are you doing?

790
01:20:46,130 --> 01:20:48,570
We haven't seen each other in a long time. Don't be so cold.

791
01:20:48,570 --> 01:20:51,310
He was brazen enough to invite everyone in Gosan.

792
01:20:51,510 --> 01:20:53,810
Most people who got invited probably won't attend the party.

793
01:20:53,810 --> 01:20:55,780
I always knew he was an amazing person.

794
01:20:55,780 --> 01:20:57,540
But I didn't know he'd become this successful.

795
01:20:57,540 --> 01:21:00,910
I bet the associate director will get jealous once she sees this.

796
01:21:01,020 --> 01:21:03,180
How could you think of coming back?

797
01:21:03,180 --> 01:21:06,520
I came back to Gosan for a good reason.

798
01:21:07,620 --> 01:21:09,490
When I'm indebted to someone,

799
01:21:10,360 --> 01:21:12,190
the right thing to do is to pay back what I owe.

